quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,Alif Lam Meem
  31,2,these are verses of the wise Book
  31,3,a guidance and mercy for those who do good
  31,4,"who establish prayer and give the purifying alms, and who are certain of the Hereafter"
  31,5,"They are rightly guided by their Lord, and they are the successful"
  31,6,"Some people prefer idle talk [over God's message] in order to lead those without knowledge away from God's path, and to ridicule it. They will have a humiliating punishment"
  31,7,"And when our verses are recited to him, he turns away arrogantly, as if he had not heard, as if there was deafness in his ears, so give him news of a painful punishment"
  31,8,Those who believe and do good deeds will have Gardens of Delight
  31,9,"where they will remain forever. This is the true promise of God, for He is the Almighty, the Wise"
  31,10,"He created the heavens without visible pillars, and firmly set mountains on earth, in case it should move under you, and spread every kind of creature over it. And We send down rain from the sky and make every kind of good plant grow"
  31,11,"This is God's creation. Show me, then, what your other gods have created. Truly, the unjust are clearly lost"